-- Assets for the per-package dk0 build: the MSVC build activator
-- (Apparatus.Dk0BuildWin) and the MlFront localize wrapper (Dk0Localize.Script).
-- Dk0.Closure drives the per-package build and the Dk0 recipe republishes
-- bin/dk0.exe. The opam lock is consumed straight from the localized MlFront
-- source (mlfront/dk.opam-lock.jsonc via Dk0.MlFrontSource), not a separate
-- checked-in copy, so it never drifts from what the archive actually ships.

### CommonsBase_Dk.Apparatus@1.0.0

  % unified.asset { name="Dk0BuildWin", file="assets/dk0/dk0-build-win.bat" }
  'asset'
  '793'
  'sha256:01498036219d67f5f28855cad32ead976d3161f33595af7e8538fa3d5b50ef15'

